  <div class="comment-content">

    <div class="edit-comment-hide">
      <div class="comment-body markdown-body markdown-format js-comment-body">
          <p>The suggested code is for creating a properly calculated cache for mobile use.</p>

<p>I checked the 0.5.0 src, the NPE is at the point of <a href="https://github.com/mapsforge/mapsforge/blob/0.5.0/mapsforge-map/src/main/java/org/mapsforge/map/layer/cache/FileSystemTileCache.java#L99">deleting</a> the cache folder at activity end.</p>

<p>Apparently during consecutive restarts, the cache folder does not have enough time to be created and we try to delete a non existed directory.</p>

<p>I pushed a fix with <a href="https://github.com/mapsforge/mapsforge/commit/7d7dd3c3954673cd47850f3955eb34b61c139d0b" class="commit-link"><tt>7d7dd3c</tt></a> at dev.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
